title: Delicious Deluxe-Dream Vacation Solitaire-Saints & Sinners Bingo
description:
3 New Wildgames

Delicious Deluxe

Roll up your sleeves for fast fun in Delicious Deluxe, a tantalizing 
restaurant challenge. Join Emily on her quest to make her dreams come 
true in two game modes and seven different restaurants. Success means 
more tables, bigger restaurants, and a menu full of uniquely delectable 
items. Tasty treats may keep your customers happy, but it's going to 
take quick clicks and careful timing to get Emily's ambitions off the 
ground. Take a bite out of Delicious Deluxe today!

Dream Vacation Solitaire

Sail from one beautiful location to the next as you play solitaire
for points and prizes in Dream Vacation Solitaire! Dream Vacation S
olitaire features over 30 games including: Sea Towers, Grandfather, 
Old Clock, Scorpion, Big Forty, Easthaven, and Blind Alleys. Making 
matches and combinations gives you access to power moves that let you 
clear the boards more easily. And if you do well enough, you'll earn 
medals, trophies, and even new yachts to sail to the next vacation paradise. 
Play 35 levels in 5 environments 

Saints and Sinners Bingo

BINGO! As a new player on the championship bingo circuit, collect special, 
lucky, charms in order to beat a group of shady tricksters. Travel to 20 
unique bingo venues and earn all 20 charms to win the day. A motley crew 
of 30 villainous opponents will try every trick to snatch your prize away, 
but there are 3 game modes and 2 paths to ensure your shot at victory. 
Saints and Sinners Bingo is a fun spin on the classic, popular game.
